/F2 22 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 794.00 Tm (UrbanVoice Project Viva Guide) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 755.00 Tm (Prepared for a 3-member group viva.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 734.00 Tm (1. Project Overview) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 705.00 Tm (UrbanVoice is an urban issue reporting platform. Citizens can report civic problems such as) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 691.00 Tm (road damage, garbage, water supply issues, electricity problems, drainage, and public safety) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 677.00 Tm (concerns. Block officers see issues from their assigned block and update progress. Admins) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 663.00 Tm (manage the whole platform, officers, citizens, and analytics.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 642.00 Tm (The project follows a MERN-style flow:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 621.00 Tm (- Frontend: React + Vite in client/) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 606.00 Tm (- Backend: Node.js + Express in server/) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 591.00 Tm (- Database: MongoDB with Mongoose models) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 576.00 Tm (- Authentication: JWT tokens, role-based routes, and session storage on frontend) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 561.00 Tm (- File uploads: Multer stores issue photos in server/uploads) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 541.00 Tm (Main user roles:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 520.00 Tm (- Citizen: Register/login, submit issue, view own reports, receive notifications.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 505.00 Tm (- Block Officer: Login, view assigned block issues, update status, flag duplicates, view) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 491.00 Tm (block analytics.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 476.00 Tm (- Admin: Login, view all issues, update/delete issues, manage officers/citizens, view) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 462.00 Tm (platform analytics.) Tj
