1 0 0 1 48.00 416.00 Tm (8. Important Security Points for Viva) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 387.00 Tm (- Passwords are never stored as plain text; they are hashed using bcrypt.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 372.00 Tm (- JWT tokens identify user id and role.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 357.00 Tm (- Backend validates every protected request using protect.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 342.00 Tm (- Role guards prevent unauthorized access even if someone changes frontend route manually.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 327.00 Tm (- Admin registration is blocked from public signup.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 312.00 Tm (- First admin seed endpoint locks after an admin already exists.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 297.00 Tm (- File upload accepts only image MIME types and limits size to 5 MB.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 282.00 Tm (- Forgot password stores hashed reset token, not raw token.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 267.00 Tm (- Axios sends token with every API request.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 62.00 252.00 Tm (- sessionStorage is used so different tabs can hold separate sessions.) Tj
